text:
Marine Parade MRT
The station was originally targeted for completion and opening in Year 2023. However, it was delayed till 2024 due to the COVID-19 Pandemic.
Clean and modern. The station is massive, length-wise. Takes about 10mins walking from one end to another. Equipped with two set of toilets, including for the disabled.

Whose idea was it to open TEL in 5 stages? What's so hard about building the train line in 1 full piece? Really need this station to open soon to access East Coast Park without having to change to buses from other train lines.
